{"lastModified":1739871378146,"uri":"c::29936054103::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656","yachtType":["Motor","Gulet"],"description":"Operating Area: Adriatic Coast, Split, Dubrovnik, Croatia\n\nDiscover the Magic of Sailing Aboard MSY ALISA – Your Perfect Family-Friendly Escape!\n\nMSY ALISA is a stunning 30-meter gulet, designed for the ultimate relaxing and adventure-filled cruise. With her spacious layout and elegant design, she offers a safe and comfortable haven, making her the ideal choice for families with children, couples, and groups of friends seeking a truly special getaway.\n\nStart your mornings admiring breathtaking views from the spacious sun deck, where you can soak up the sun, unwind with a book, or simply enjoy the gentle sea breeze. The stern deck is perfect for relaxation and socializing, whether you're savoring delicious local delicacies, sharing laughter over drinks, or indulging in a peaceful moment while gazing at the horizon.\n\nA highlight of every day is the outdoor dining experience, where a large table becomes the heart of the journey—bringing people together over authentic Croatian cuisine, fresh seafood, and unforgettable moments.\n\nWith six beautifully designed cabins (4 double and 2 triple), ALISA comfortably accommodates up to 14 guests. All cabins are located at the front of the vessel, ensuring a private and tranquil retreat. Each cabin is fully air-conditioned and features its own en-suite bathroom with a shower for maximum comfort.\n\nSailing on MSY ALISA means exploring the best of the Adriatic—from historic coastal towns rich in culture to secluded bays perfect for daily swimming and relaxation. Swim in crystal-clear waters, kayak along untouched shorelines, snorkel among vibrant marine life, or simply enjoy the serenity of the open sea.\n\nWhether you seek adventure, relaxation, or a perfect balance of both, MSY ALISA promises an unforgettable experience filled with natural beauty, cultural discoveries, and cherished moments with loved ones.\n\nJoin us and create memories that will last a lifetime! ⛵🌊☀️","blueprint":{"name":"ALISA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ee02920-ead6-11ef-a51c-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ee38480-ead6-11ef-a51c-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ec267f0-ead6-11ef-a51b-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ec240e0-ead6-11ef-a51c-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6f1ae830-ead6-11ef-a51d-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ef5acf0-ead6-11ef-9402-ef90fdfdbe56/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ef510b0-ead6-11ef-9153-956b88602188/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ef585e0-ead6-11ef-a51c-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ef81df1-ead6-11ef-a51c-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6f91c5e0-ead6-11ef-a51e-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6efa8ef0-ead6-11ef-a9af-7d0dbe5d1e88/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6efa40d0-ead6-11ef-9153-956b88602188/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6efbc770-ead6-11ef-a51d-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::330be750-ead0-11ef-bd2b-a52ca1bf1656::assets::6ee27310-ead6-11ef-a51c-f584f378c9e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image: